  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Works on 64bit Windows, Linux(SteamOS) and MacOS(both ARM & Intel)!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196320/extras/cf9ae04d4a2fd267d295706af52f7c54.poster.avif?t=1741438064\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196320/extras/cf9ae04d4a2fd267d295706af52f7c54.webm?t=1741438064\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196320/extras/cf9ae04d4a2fd267d295706af52f7c54.mp4?t=1741438064\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Space Yugoslav is an old school 2D shooter where you play as a bounty hunter named Nada. Survive another night at your very risky job and get back home with your space Stoyadin in one piece.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196320/extras/c5b959466a656f889ec3d5a0afb1b17e.poster.avif?t=1741438064\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196320/extras/c5b959466a656f889ec3d5a0afb1b17e.webm?t=1741438064\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196320/extras/c5b959466a656f889ec3d5a0afb1b17e.mp4?t=1741438064\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Your mission is to save non-alignment space colonies from space police raids. Escape bullets, shoot the police out of the colonies, earn some extra money, drive your Stoyadin through space and get back to your love at home, as soon as possible.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196320/extras/b62cdcd00444af797840cc723ea25238.poster.avif?t=1741438064\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196320/extras/b62cdcd00444af797840cc723ea25238.webm?t=1741438064\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196320/extras/b62cdcd00444af797840cc723ea25238.mp4?t=1741438064\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196320/extras/eb55eed59bcea43000c49e11fe15dc2b.poster.avif?t=1741438064\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196320/extras/eb55eed59bcea43000c49e11fe15dc2b.webm?t=1741438064\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196320/extras/eb55eed59bcea43000c49e11fe15dc2b.mp4?t=1741438064\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>\"great game you shoot you fly you die you win, its short sweet and simple\" - Yugoslavz</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196320/extras/df397cd816bc179fd2b79888381dcac6.poster.avif?t=1741438064\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196320/extras/df397cd816bc179fd2b79888381dcac6.webm?t=1741438064\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196320/extras/df397cd816bc179fd2b79888381dcac6.mp4?t=1741438064\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196320/extras/0864651a75d248757e6630ed5e943f0d.poster.avif?t=1741438064\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196320/extras/0864651a75d248757e6630ed5e943f0d.webm?t=1741438064\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196320/extras/0864651a75d248757e6630ed5e943f0d.mp4?t=1741438064\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>\"101 / 100\" - тони пони</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196320/extras/746c2b608945cb5430f1cb6c959e8bc9.poster.avif?t=1741438064\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196320/extras/746c2b608945cb5430f1cb6c959e8bc9.webm?t=1741438064\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196320/extras/746c2b608945cb5430f1cb6c959e8bc9.mp4?t=1741438064\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
